  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/21d155d022cf285b378f19aacdb6f9c9.poster.avif?t=1771864748\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/21d155d022cf285b378f19aacdb6f9c9.webm?t=1771864748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/21d155d022cf285b378f19aacdb6f9c9.mp4?t=1771864748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/15ecaf1f71c98b62dec01a482513682b.avif?t=1771864748\" width=620 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The descent into horror begins...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You come to your senses in an unknown place. Everything around seems familiar, but memories slip away like sand through your fingers. The only thing left is to move forward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/ebcadcd5ccc8f6e2d0a296c2a9825936.poster.avif?t=1771864748\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/ebcadcd5ccc8f6e2d0a296c2a9825936.webm?t=1771864748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/ebcadcd5ccc8f6e2d0a296c2a9825936.mp4?t=1771864748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An inner voice tells you: <strong>you are a famous writer, the “king of horror,” whose stories made readers shudder with fear. </strong>But now reality is much more frightening than the worst nightmares that came from your pen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/586f54b72468f989b95a88e38a648c18.poster.avif?t=1771864748\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/586f54b72468f989b95a88e38a648c18.webm?t=1771864748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/586f54b72468f989b95a88e38a648c18.mp4?t=1771864748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What kind of place is this? Who's playing with your mind? Each discovery brings you closer to the solution, but at the same time opens the door to even more sinister depths. Time loses its meaning, and the line between fiction and reality blurs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you ready to face your own fears?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/8f55036c51ffec8e07282036949f91d7.poster.avif?t=1771864748\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/8f55036c51ffec8e07282036949f91d7.webm?t=1771864748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/8f55036c51ffec8e07282036949f91d7.mp4?t=1771864748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/b033b14a13382f7a934e65da0b79bd69.avif?t=1771864748\" width=620 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Carefully examine</strong> everything around you; details play a crucial role in uncovering what happened here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve <strong>simple</strong> <strong>puzzles</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/82791c616f79ad5b4d885905199b1778.poster.avif?t=1771864748\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/82791c616f79ad5b4d885905199b1778.webm?t=1771864748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/82791c616f79ad5b4d885905199b1778.mp4?t=1771864748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beware of the monster</strong>; it is always somewhere nearby.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use the camera</strong> as a tool for solving puzzles — it will reveal what is hidden from the eye.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/3b06c460819be64019817b347eb695a2.poster.avif?t=1771864748\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/3b06c460819be64019817b347eb695a2.webm?t=1771864748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/3b06c460819be64019817b347eb695a2.mp4?t=1771864748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/2a2b6d7c635f9131df775cf74bddf1d4.avif?t=1771864748\" width=620 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. The game has autosave.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. Realistic graphics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. High-quality sound design.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4. Simple but interesting puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5. Average game completion time: 30-60 minutes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6. Genre: Walking Simulator.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399670/extras/34f615cda2e5300ddc03f5e2ea9ef120.avif?t=1771864748\" width=620 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features machine translation into the following languages:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- French</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- German</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Spanish</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Portuguese (Brazilian)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Chinese (Simplified)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Korean</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Polish</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Japanese</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
